<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_9952043eb192.aspx"><b>蝃蝀</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson9952043eb192">
蝃蝀在东，莫之敢指。女子有行，远父母兄弟。<br />朝隮于西，崇朝其雨。女子有行，远兄弟父母。<br />乃如之人也，怀婚姻也。大无信也，不知命也！
